name: Remove SKUs Category Tags
author: Asif Ali

sections.description:
Description: This plugin will Remove Woocommerce product SKUs Category Tags woocommerce Product Details Page.

Feature

  • This plugin will Remove Woocommerce product SKUs Category Tags
    woocommerce Product Details Page.
sections.installation:
1. Upload the folder “hide-sku-category-tags” to “/wp-content/plugins/” path.
  2. Activate the plugin through the “Plugins” menu in WordPress backend
  3. After activating the plugin, product SKUs Category Tags will be Remove.
  4. Enjoy!
sections.faq:
1. Intall and activate plugin SKUs Category Tags will be Remove.
  2. No technical skills needed.
sections.changelog: This is first version with no known errors found
